    "content": "LET ME LOVE YOU by MARIO\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIntro: ALL BARRE CHORDS\r\n\r\n Am           G               F\r\nMmmm ..ah...Mmmmm....Yeah....Mmmmm....Yeah, Yeah, Yeah\r\n\r\n Am           G               F                  Am\r\nMmmm ..ah...Mmmmm....Yeah....Mmmmm....Yeah-e-Yeah\r\n\r\n\r\nVERSE:\r\n                       G\r\nBaby I just don't get it \r\n\r\n                         F\r\nDo you enjoy being hurt? \r\n\r\n                                                         Am\r\nI know you smelled the perfume, the make-up on his shirt\r\n\r\n                              G\r\nYou don't believe his stories\r\n\r\n                               F\r\nYou know that they're all lies\r\n\r\n                                                          Am\r\nBad as you are you stick around and I just don't know why\r\n\r\n                           G\r\nIf I was ya man (baby you)\r\n                             F\r\nNever worry bout (what I do)\r\n                                \r\nI'd be coming home (back to you)\r\n\r\n                             Am\r\nEvery night, doin' you right \r\n\r\n                                                G\r\nYou're the type of woman (deserves good thangs)\r\n\r\n                                           F\r\nFist full of diamonds (hand full of rings)\r\n\r\nBaby you're a star (I just want to show you,you are) \r\n\r\n\r\nCHORUS:\r\n                  Am\r\nYou should let me love you \r\n\r\n              G                   F   \r\nLet me be the one to give you everything you want and need\r\n\r\n                      Am\r\nBaby good love and protection \r\n\r\n               G\r\nMake me your selection \r\n\r\n                 F\r\nShow you the way love's supposed to be \r\n\r\n                       Am                  G         F\r\nBaby you should let me love you, love you, love you...loooove you\r\n\r\n    \r\nyeah \r\n\r\n\r\nVERSE:\r\nAm\r\nListen\r\n                              G                           F\r\nYour true beauty's description looks so good that it hurts \r\n\r\nYou're a dime plus ninety-nine and it's a shame \r\n                                  Am\r\nDon't even know what you're worth \r\n\r\n                  G\r\nEverywhere you go they stop and stare \r\n\r\n                              F\r\nCause you're bad and it shows \r\n\r\n                                                           Am\r\nFrom your head to your toes, Out of control, baby you know \r\n\r\n                           G\r\nIf I was ya man (baby you)\r\n\r\n                             F\r\nNever worry bout (what I do)\r\n\r\nI'd be coming home (back to you)\r\n\r\n                            Am\r\nEvery night doin' you right \r\n\r\n                                                G\r\nYou're the type of woman (deserves good thangs)\r\n                                         \r\n                                           F\r\nFist full of diamonds (hand full of rings)\r\n\r\nBaby you're a star (I just want to show you, you are) \r\n\r\nCHORUS\r\n\r\nSPECIAL THANKS TO THIS GUY, I COPIED IT OFF HIM AND MADE CHORDS EASIER\r\nTabbed by Jan Schacht\r\nNovember 10th, 2004\r\njan@derjan.com\r\nHamburg - Germany\r\n\r\nCOMMENT: ryanelperez@yahoo.com",
